en: It could be dangerous to topple these boxes over.
A large pile of boxes that goes all the way to the ceiling.
zh_TW: 一大疊疊到天花板的箱子。

en: This room feels different...
Is it safe...?
Ah, there you are.
Who are you...? What is this place?
Straight to the point I see.
Well, this isn't quite your world.
zh_TW: 是這樣的，這裡不是妳們的世界。

en: ...What?
Let's not get into it. You're doing a ritual, correct?
zh_TW: 不需要深究。你剛剛在舉行儀式，沒有錯吧？

en: Stop, and go home.
All of you. I mean it.
Excuse me...?
Kat, if you keep doing what you're doing, things won't end well.
zh_TW: 凱特，如果妳繼續這麼下去，下場不會很好。

en: Do you know this person, Kat?
Not at all.
They seem to know you, though.
zh_TW: 可是他似乎知道妳是誰。

en: What is it with everyone warning me lately?
zh_TW: 為什麼大家最近一直給我警告？

en: I need some answers.
So far, you haven't-
Stop! Don't cross that line.
Sigh...
If you haven't realized by now, the ritual works.
zh_TW: 如果妳還沒有意會過來，儀式是有用的。

en: It will take you somewhere you'll never return from.
zh_TW: 它會把妳帶到妳永遠無法回來的地方。

en: If it works then... I should definitely finish it.
zh_TW: 如果它有用…我一定會完成它。

en: Kat, what are you saying...?
Sorry, but I can't listen to this person. I have my reasons for doing this.
zh_TW: 抱歉，但是我無法相信這個人。我做這些事是有理由的。

en: I don't know how much you value what you have right now but...
zh_TW: 我不知道妳怎麼看待妳現在擁有的…

en: If you continue down this path, you'll lose everything.
zh_TW: 如果妳繼續下去，妳會失去一切。

en: Everything you hold dear, and everything you don't.
zh_TW: 妳珍惜的一切，還有不在乎的。

en: Your questions will not receive any satisfying answers...
zh_TW: 妳的問題不會得到任何滿意的解答。

en: And everything you know about the world will turn meaningless.
zh_TW: 而妳對世界的瞭解都會變得毫無意義。

en: Those three.
Are you willing to sacrifice their lives for your so-called "reasons"?
zh_TW: 妳願意為了妳的"理由"犧牲她們的性命嗎？

en: Lives...?
Furthermore, your own life.
Are you wiling to die for the answers you're seeking?
zh_TW: 妳願意為妳找尋的解答而死嗎？

en: Let's go back, Kat.
I want to leave...
I don't believe you. Why don't you just give me my answers yourself then? Spare me the trip.
zh_TW: 我不相信你。你為什麼不自己給我解答呢？省得我麻煩。

en: I thought so.
I've said what I needed to.
zh_TW: 我已經說完我需要說的了。

en: Why? Who are you?
Just someone who has seen too many humans die.
zh_TW: 只是個看到太多人類死去的人。

en: It would sadden me to add you four to the pile.
zh_TW: 把你們四個加上會讓我難過。

en: Go home, Kat.
Can't you feel it in the air here? You're all in danger.
zh_TW: 妳們感覺不到嗎？妳們都在危險當中。

en: Kat, please, this feels too dangerous...
zh_TW: 凱特，求求妳，這感覺太危險了…

en: Kat, let's just go.
Yeah, let's get out of here. I didn't sign up for this.
zh_TW: 對啊，我們離開這裡吧。我不打算加入。

en: Kat, we don't want something bad to happen to you.
zh_TW: 凱特，我們不希望妳出什麼事。

en: Fine, let's go.
Are you by any chance the same person from my dream earlier today?
zh_TW: 你是不是也是我之前夢到的人？

en: A dream...?
It must have been your subconscious warning you as well.
zh_TW: 那一定是妳的潛意識也在警告妳。

en: ...I see.
(Oh.)
(Should I give this person the blueprints I found...?)
zh_TW: (我應該把我發現的藍圖給這個人嗎…？)

en: Yes
No
By the way...
I found these weird blueprints a few minutes ago.
zh_TW: 我幾分鐘前找到了這些奇怪的藍圖。

en: Just take them.
Otherwise I might change my mind.
Huh... this is...
Thank you.
You're doing the right thing, Kat. Your father would be glad.
zh_TW: 妳這麼做是對的，凱特。妳的父親會很高興的。

en: It's okay to accept the life you're left with. Don't destroy it.
zh_TW: 接受妳生命中剩餘的部分是沒關係的。別毀了它。

en: ...I guess.
Kat!!!
Go already. You can't be here.
zh_TW: 快走吧，妳們不該出現在這裡。

en: If what you said is true...
Then thanks.
I'll pass on the ritual.
For tonight.
That's good enough.
A large pile of trash cans. They all seem to be empty.
zh_TW: 一大堆垃圾桶。它們看起來是空的。
